    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p /><p /><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"501dfe74-d3ec-461a-ada0-d6add20844d9\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;\">\n<p><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-inverse\">Analytic Lights</span></strong></p>\n</div></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManStudio_Header_1.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/631242816/RenderManStudio_Header_1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761237165792&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=410\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/631242816/RenderManStudio_Header_1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761237165792&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1998\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"631242824\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManStudio_Header_1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"631242816\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"aafaa562-05c7-4a3f-9bb8-c6dc2ad0a414\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/631242816/RenderManStudio_Header_1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761237165792&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=820 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/631242816/RenderManStudio_Header_1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761237165792&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=410 1x\"></span><p>RenderMan includes a set of built-in basic geometric lights. These specialized shapes - <strong>DomeLight, DistantLight, RectLight, DiscLight, </strong>and<strong> SphereLight</strong><em><strong> </strong></em>(particularly the latter two) - can provide superior sampling behavior, compared with arbitrary geometry.</p><p /><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"862e4523-28fb-4ff4-9d05-f3c3be5b6d8b\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;\">\n<p><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-inverse\">Mesh Lights</span></strong></p>\n</div></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_MeshLights.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/631242816/RenderMan_MeshLights.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761237366913&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=409\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/631242816/RenderMan_MeshLights.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761237366913&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1069\" data-width=\"1984\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"631177265\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_MeshLights.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"631242816\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"de093be5-05c9-4e55-9f77-8838b9f1bd7d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/631242816/RenderMan_MeshLights.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761237366913&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=818 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/631242816/RenderMan_MeshLights.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761237366913&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=409 1x\"></span><p>These are great for using arbitrary shapes in lighting. These consume more memory since they are geometry and complex shapes, which may increase noise. These can make use of visibility like any other object: camera, shadow/transmission, and indirect visibility.</p><p /><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"2e85b92d-ea98-48f8-a2af-aa013bf6f2a7\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;\">\n<p><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-inverse\">Emissive Surfaces</span></strong></p>\n</div></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Glow.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/631242816/RenderMan_Glow.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761237671203&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/631242816/RenderMan_Glow.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761237671203&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"631177272\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Glow.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"631242816\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"8df90ef6-c9a4-4107-854a-1e23819677df\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/631242816/RenderMan_Glow.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761237671203&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/631242816/RenderMan_Glow.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761237671203&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\"></span><p>These typically use a constant bxdf or &quot;glow&quot; parameter to indirectly light a scene. This is inefficient and should usually be avoided, but it may be helpful for texture-mapping &quot;lights&quot; onto futuristic objects and panels with low emission values.</p><p>If you want to do this efficiently, try using a textured mesh light</p>"
    }
